This page demonstrates how Starlight natively handles multiple files using the `{% tabs %}` and `{% tabitem %}` tags in Markdoc.

{% tabs %}
{% tabitem label="index.js" %}
```javascript
// This is index.js
console.log("Hello from index.js!");

function welcome() {
  console.log("Welcome to Novadesk");
}

welcome();
```
{% /tabitem %}

{% tabitem label="style.css" %}
```css
/* This is style.css */
body {
  background-color: #f0f0f0;
  color: #333;
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
}

.widget-container {
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}
```
{% /tabitem %}
{% /tabs %}

